column1: IF ccr_l7b_estradiol_d is MF 0 AND ccr_sa_thb_d is MF 2 AND ccr_thb_d is MF 2 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
IF ccr_zoa_dhf_d is MF 1 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 1
IF ccr_l6a_oh_dha_d is MF 0 AND ccr_estriol_d is MF 0 THEN 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1
IF ccr_s_ad_17b_d is MF 0 THEN 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0
IF ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 2 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 0
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 0  2_Normal is 1  3_Surpoid is 0  4_Obese is 1  5_ExtremeObese is 0
